Title: Terraria Save Game Editor
Description:
TSGE, Terraria Save Game Editor, allows users to modify save game files for the popular game, Terraria.

TSGE is written in C# using WPF.
HomeWiki:
TSGE for Terraria 1.3.0.x is now released on the EliteMMO Network here:
http://www.elitemmonetwork.com/forums/
